00:01:00.139 --> 00:01:05.900
while there I was the chair of the math department and in charge of the engineering program,

00:01:05.900 --> 00:01:13.379
and I also created one of the nation's first certificates in practical data science at

00:01:13.379 --> 00:01:18.180
a community college.

