So I have created a GitHub that contains all of the materials that are relevant to this

00:01:31.779 --> 00:01:38.099
talk, it's also a work in progress, I'm actually trying to put together some materials that

00:01:38.099 --> 00:01:46.139
can turn into a one cohesive thing that a teacher can then just use as a handbook for

00:01:46.139 --> 00:01:53.699
any stats class and any textbook that they might choose to use.

